highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 266 weeks straight.
Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Lo Siento BB:/ (with Bad Bunny & Julieta Venegas)” is the highest at #28.
“Bam Bam (feat. Ed Sheeran)” by Camila Cabello and Ed Sheeran is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #14.
“Jordan” by Ryan Castro is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 73 spots at #100.
